message: Hey Guys! I am living in The Marshall Apartments in Dinky Town next year with Collin Humpal and Nick Anderson. We are all Freshmen right now and next fall we will be Sophomores. We are currently looking for another person for our last roommate to accommodate our 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms apartment. Also, right next door to us we will have 4 guys (Hayden Wilson, Alec McElhinny, Christopher Cornish, and Axl Harlander) who are also fellow believers and we assembled a Gospel Community called the "Marshall Men." The rent is $570 a month with everything included plus amazing amenities. The only thing that is not included is gas and electric which is typical for an apartment which is usually $15-$20 a month. Please reach out to one of us if you or anyone you know is interested or just have questions. Thanks!
